Ignite IRCd install process:
----------------------------

1.) Run the configure script so we can collect some information about your system.
       ./configure
2.) Edit "include/config.h" to define/undefine features and settings of Ignite.
3.) Execute "make" to build Ignite.
4.) Execute "make install" to install Ignite to the path defined in config.h (DPATH).
5.) Edit ircd.conf to suit your needs.
6.) Launch the Ignite ircd executable and enjoy. =)
